{"word":"G4962 - συστρέφω - systréphō - soos-tref'-o - Gather","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συστρέφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">systréphō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soos-tref'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Gather</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to twist together, roll together"},{"paragraph":"2. to collect, combine, unite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4762 - στρέφω - stréphō - stref'-o/4762\">G4762</a>; to <i>twist together</i>, that is, <i>collect</i> (a bundle, a crowd): - gather.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}